  "detailed_description": "Bringing roguelike mechanics to classic word games. Plan your turns carefully to rack up points and multipliers to earn the best medals available. Use your winnings in the shop to build out your abilities and allow you to tackle tougher opponents.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/08a32119f0668f932a275bc56dc5a94f.poster.avif?t=1735928005\" width=274 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/08a32119f0668f932a275bc56dc5a94f.webm?t=1735928005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/08a32119f0668f932a275bc56dc5a94f.mp4?t=1735928005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Purchase powerful relics to enhance and customize your runs. </strong><br>Build up your points and multipliers. Buy relics that push you to new and unique strategies. Break the rules and do things you have never done in a word game before.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/15b735153ccf660fcb315f2784f0c74e.avif?t=1735928005\" width=616 height=149 /></span><br><br><strong>Entreat the gods to build a unique approach to your run.</strong><br>Enhance your tiles with more points and unique abilities. Customize your board to suit your play style and approach. Go beyond letters adding ! and ? tiles to your bag.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/1e2394d22be89aceb36b4f45642555da.poster.avif?t=1735928005\" width=280 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/1e2394d22be89aceb36b4f45642555da.webm?t=1735928005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/1e2394d22be89aceb36b4f45642555da.mp4?t=1735928005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Take on a wide variety of new unlocking challenges.</strong><br>New medals mean new challenges. Each medal has its own starting board, roster of opponents and pool of items to find. Advance through both more difficult matches and medals featuring unique challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/978677d1440e61b35e300d16942b7d87.avif?t=1735928005\" width=616 height=144 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Bringing roguelike mechanics to classic word games. Plan your turns carefully to rack up points and multipliers to earn the best medals available. Use your winnings in the shop to build out your abilities and allow you to tackle tougher opponents.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/08a32119f0668f932a275bc56dc5a94f.poster.avif?t=1735928005\" width=274 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/08a32119f0668f932a275bc56dc5a94f.webm?t=1735928005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/08a32119f0668f932a275bc56dc5a94f.mp4?t=1735928005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Purchase powerful relics to enhance and customize your runs. </strong><br>Build up your points and multipliers. Buy relics that push you to new and unique strategies. Break the rules and do things you have never done in a word game before.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/15b735153ccf660fcb315f2784f0c74e.avif?t=1735928005\" width=616 height=149 /></span><br><br><strong>Entreat the gods to build a unique approach to your run.</strong><br>Enhance your tiles with more points and unique abilities. Customize your board to suit your play style and approach. Go beyond letters adding ! and ? tiles to your bag.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/1e2394d22be89aceb36b4f45642555da.poster.avif?t=1735928005\" width=280 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/1e2394d22be89aceb36b4f45642555da.webm?t=1735928005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/1e2394d22be89aceb36b4f45642555da.mp4?t=1735928005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Take on a wide variety of new unlocking challenges.</strong><br>New medals mean new challenges. Each medal has its own starting board, roster of opponents and pool of items to find. Advance through both more difficult matches and medals featuring unique challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884080/extras/978677d1440e61b35e300d16942b7d87.avif?t=1735928005\" width=616 height=144 /></span>",
